name: Soro - The village pub

reviews.review_text: Good place to party on a Saturday night. The place gets filled around midnight, but the food isn’t too good. Also you’ll have to get a card and then it recharged and then only you can use it to order food or drinks. Also the left over money is non refundable so top it up accordingly only.

Great music, elite crowd, good food, salsa dance mostly.There is no cover charge but you have to get advance refill card against which you can order. Minimum Rs500 to top up card but interesting to note here is there is no refund if there is a balance left

We tried the snapper and broccoli which was delicious. Cocktails are very innovative. The staff is very efficient and quick. Very much kids friendly. Best place for sundowner in Anjuna. Great spot. Has a roof top or place right next to the beach. Great parking place.

description:
### A Night at Soro - The Village Pub: A Dance and Dine Paradise in Siolim

Nestled in the vibrant locale of Siolim, *Soro - The Village Pub* stands out with an impressive rating of **4.2** from over **4,239 reviews**. Renowned for its buzz-worthy atmosphere, this establishment has become a staple for those seeking nightlife infused with delectable food, a lively crowd, and captivating dance sessions. Customers have frequently highlighted tags such as **crowd** (102 mentions), **dance** (95 mentions), and **salsa** (50 mentions), painting a picture of an energetic yet enjoyable experience.

### Ambiance & Design
Upon stepping into Soro, patrons are welcomed by a delightful yet eclectic mix of rustic and modern décor that exudes a charming village pub vibe. The lighting strikes a perfect balance: dim enough to encourage intimate conversations but bright enough to highlight the vibrant crowd enjoying their night out. One look at the visuals reveals a spacious venue with cozy seating arrangements that allow guests to revel in both the dining experience and the energetic salsa music wafting through the air. The covered rooftop and proximity to the beach offer patrons stunning views—a perfect backdrop for a sunset drink. 

![Soro Rooftop Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlDKAhh_3VMS59j5nu288rt5PJFO4zBYcgcEXu0QfdXzvuhwTsETCuFWTptSWYV7A22C47AIz_o1zPbEFKddxi5Fe_2S0ewP4ji4EozW28LBnn1XqGen0-spaC6iyqU1vJkR9MJ=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience
The culinary offerings at Soro are as exciting as its atmosphere. While some customers have expressed mixed feelings about the food, others have significantly endorsed dishes like **snapper with broccoli**, praised for its deliciousness. Innovative cocktails also steal the show, providing an enticing array for those looking to unwind. Patrons should note that food and drink orders are placed via a precharged card system, which has received feedback for being both engaging and slightly inconvenient due to the non-refundable balance.

![Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnzGMpkGJKFwDHCyvHW2xMI2_7ibD2VCgxGZi5LXyRgjmqopyTu0_zLB0Ns5a3BX8AMxjzcP65KMLCsggOTgjeNdv8TPjrjWsKUhlt6WO0v28rCnGlDGFPwcM13haho8zLjFHUG=w375-h563-p)

### Customer Experience & Service
The customer service at Soro is noted for being efficient and prompt, making it a family-friendly option—a welcome surprise at such a lively venue. While the Saturday night crowd can create a bustling environment, the staff's professionalism stands out, ensuring that customers feel valued regardless of the rush. The absence of a cover charge is a significant draw, though guests must be prepared to manage their preloaded spending cards wisely.

### Popularity & Reviews
The buzz surrounding Soro can be felt both in person and across social media platforms, where patrons share their experiences, particularly highlighting the salsa dance events that sparkle bright on the weekend. While the food may have its highs and lows per individual palates, the overall vibe keeps the energy flowing, drawing various crowds ready to let loose. Many reviews refer to it as a prime location for sundowners, further emphasizing its appeal. 

### Visual Highlights
The customer-submitted photos enhance the narrative of Soro’s ambiance and menu. From glimpses of animated crowds dancing under colorful lights to visually enticing dishes, the images serve as a vivid testament to what visitors can expect. One image captures the dynamic essence of the venue, showcasing the energy and fun that awaits.

![Dancing and Crowd](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkqvju0EAaQLfbX-wR3vnhUDqS871Tnu42QUUG6vOgWFbhY7VPIv8TF-xTqAsBmobx_dPp6UMzxgVtHxJiZeiwY5Ft-6qXB24shce9AsVWkHT9dtMNPV5KFUAApCy19sTVyq_Cq=w375-h281-p)

In conclusion, *Soro - The Village Pub* effectively combines nightlife excitement with a relaxed dining atmosphere, making it an essential stop for anyone looking to enjoy a magical Saturday night in Siolim. Whether you're there for the food, the dance, or to chill with friends, Soro promises an experience filled with fun, flavor, and festivities.
